                    <div class="inline-flex items-center px-4 py-2 bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/20 rounded-full mb-6">
                        <span class="text-white text-sm font-medium">E-Commerce Giant</span>
                    </div>
                    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-white mb-6">
                        Amazon: E-Commerce Excellence
                    </h1>
                    <p class="text-xl text-white/90 mb-8">
                        The world's largest online marketplace offering millions of products with exceptional shopping experience, personalized recommendations, and global logistics excellence.
                    </p>
                    <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-6">
                        <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-xl p-4">
                            <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-white">35%</div>
