                    Amazon is the world's largest online marketplace offering millions of products with global reach and top-tier logistics. 
                    From books to electronics, fashion to groceries, Amazon has become the go-to destination for online shopping. The platform 
                    combines cutting-edge technology with customer-obsessed service delivery, setting the gold standard for e-commerce worldwide. 
                    With features like one-click ordering, personalized recommendations, and same-day delivery, Amazon continues to innovate and 
                    shape the future of retail.
                </p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Client Goals -->
        <section class="py-16 bg-gray-50">
            <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
