                        <p class="text-gray-600">Enable easy browsing and discovery across millions of products in thousands of categories.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm border border-gray-200">
                        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-green-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
                            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M11.049 2.927c.3-.921 1.603-.921 1.902 0l1.519 4.674a1 1 0 00.95.69h4.915c.969 0 1.371 1.24.588 1.81l-3.976 2.888a1 1 0 00-.363 1.118l1.518 4.674c.3.922-.755 1.688-1.538 1.118l-3.976-2.888a1 1 0 00-1.176 0l-3.976 2.888c-.783.57-1.838-.197-1.538-1.118l1.518-4.674a1 1 0 00-.363-1.118l-3.976-2.888c-.784-.57-.38-1.81.588-1.81h4.914a1 1 0 00.951-.69l1.519-4.674z"></path>
                            </svg>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Personalized Recommendations</h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-600">Provide intelligent product recommendations that increase customer satisfaction and sales.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Challenges -->
        <section class="py-16 bg-white">
            <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
                <div class="flex items-center mb-8">
                    <div class="w-12 h-1 bg-orange-600 mr-4"></div>
                    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900">Challenges</h2>
                </div>
                <div class="space-y-4">
                    <div class="flex items-start bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-6">
                        <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-orange-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mr-4">
                            <span class="text-white font-bold">1</span>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Managing Millions of Products & Categories</h3>
                            <p class="text-gray-600">Building a system to organize, search, and display millions of products efficiently with advanced filtering capabilities.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex items-start bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-6">
                        <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-orange-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mr-4">
                            <span class="text-white font-bold">2</span>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Ensuring Secure, Smooth Checkout</h3>
                            <p class="text-gray-600">Creating a frictionless checkout process while maintaining highest security standards for payment processing.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex items-start bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-6">
                        <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-orange-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mr-4">
                            <span class="text-white font-bold">3</span>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Handling Huge Traffic Spikes</h3>
                            <p class="text-gray-600">Managing massive traffic surges during festive sales and promotional events without service degradation.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Solution -->
        <section class="py-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-50 to-gray-100">
