                            </svg>
                            <p class="text-gray-700">Personalization based on browsing history and purchase behavior drives repeat purchases.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex items-start">
                            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-orange-600 mr-3 flex-shrink-0 mt-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
                            </svg>
                            <p class="text-gray-700">Efficient search with autocomplete and filters is key to quick product discovery and customer satisfaction.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-lg">
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Implementation Approach</h3>
                    <div class="space-y-6">
                        <div class="border-l-4 border-orange-600 pl-6">
                            <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Ultra-Fast Site Performance</h4>
                            <p class="text-gray-700">Optimized CDN delivery, edge caching, and lazy loading ensuring lightning-fast page loads globally.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="border-l-4 border-blue-600 pl-6">
                            <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Smart Recommendation Engine</h4>
                            <p class="text-gray-700">Machine learning algorithms analyzing user behavior, purchase history, and trending products for personalized suggestions.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="border-l-4 border-purple-600 pl-6">
                            <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Secure Multi-Layered Checkout</h4>
                            <p class="text-gray-700">PCI-compliant payment processing with one-click ordering, saved addresses, and multiple payment options.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="border-l-4 border-green-600 pl-6">
                            <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Robust Microservices Architecture</h4>
                            <p class="text-gray-700">Scalable backend with independent services for catalog, inventory, orders, payments, and recommendations.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Results -->
        <section class="py-16 bg-white">
            <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
                <div class="flex items-center mb-8">
                    <div class="w-12 h-1 bg-orange-600 mr-4"></div>
                    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900">Results & Impact</h2>
                </div>
                <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-8">
                    <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-orange-50 to-orange-100 rounded-2xl p-8 text-center">
                        <div class="text-5xl font-bold text-orange-600 mb-2">35%</div>
                        <div class="text-gray-700 font-semibold">Increase in Repeat Customers</div>
                        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-2">Personalization drives customer loyalty</p>
